data.description: A beauty! This Large 2 story home with lots of room features an Island in kitchen, 2 large living areas, 2 dinning areas, huge master bedroom with large walk-in closet, split from other bedrooms, but close enough if needed for the concern. When the home was built in 2006 the Owner included the extra radiant barrier heat guard in attic to hopefully cut down on utility bills. The Back patio faces the east for afternoon and early evening entertainment., This home must be designed for you. A must see Home! Brokered And Advertised By: A-1 Golden Key Listing Agent: John Rabon
